description: Never add Cursor as git co-author or contributor
alwaysApply: true
---

# No Cursor co-author attribution

- NEVER add `Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>` or any Cursor co-author trailer to commit messages.
- NEVER set git author/committer to cursoragent or Cursor.
- Commits must use only the repository owner's identity.
- When committing, use a plain message with no co-author trailers.
